name: phase boa pro step on
description: Last year we took the Phase franchise to the next level with the Phase BOA Pro, and this year we're continuing the progression with a Step On model. We added top-of-the-line tech to the simple, skate-inspired upper, starting with the BOA Fit System paired with our patent-pending SUPERLOCK heel harness to eliminate heel slip and deliver a more responsive ride. We also fitted it with our R3 liner with PrimaLoft insulation, our warmest and most responsive ever. Simply put, the Phase Boa Pro Step On is one of our most advanced boots ever^PRODUCT FEATURES: Step On[R] Outsole^Dual BOA[R] Fit System with H4 Coiler Tongue Dial and Internal Ankle Harness Controlled By Remote BOA[R] Dial^PrimaLoft[R] insulation^Response Liner III^Molded IMPACT-ALG Insole^BOA[R] Silver SS Laces^FLEX RATING 5/10

name: judge
description: We put the team-favorite Judge Boot through the ringer year after year - testing, tweaking, and always making improvements with input from our riders. We added the eco-friendly and ultra-comfy molded IMPACT-ALGT insole for added comfort and better heel hold. The Judge also features our most advanced R3 liner-with PrimaLoft insulation and Aerotech ventilation to maintain the perfect foot temperature in any conditions. The Vibram outsole keeps the boot grippy yet light, while the Dual Zone BOA Fit System delivers a micro-adjustable, precision fit, engineered to perform in the toughest conditions. name: phantom
description: An OG style from 2001, the Phantom represented the best snow tech of the day, but we modernized it with top-of-the-line features for today's rider. Our ultra-responsive R3 liner is built with PrimaLoft insulation and the Aerotech ventilation system to maintain the perfect foot temperature in any conditions. The molded IMPACT-ALGT insole isn't just eco-friendly, it also provides perfect cushioning and heel hold. And on the outside we added the Dual Zone BOA Fit System which delivers a micro-adjustable, precision fit, engineered to perform in the toughest conditions. Today's Phantom is dripping in DC Snow heritage and ready to perform on the mountain. No wonder it's a favorite of so many of DC's team riders^PRODUCT FEATURES: Dual BOA[R] Fit System with Multi-color H4 Coiler Dials^Vibram[R] Outsole^Response Liner III^PrimaLoft[R] insulation^Aerotech Ventilation System^Molded IMPACT-ALG Insole^Internal Ankle Harness^Leather Tongue Overlay^BOA[R] Silver SS Laces^FLEX RATING 8/10
